In python first install flask 
command - pip3 install Flask in linux and for windows pip install Flask
Then create a virtual enviornment 
pip install virtualenv 
command -> virtualenv . for linux and (virtualenv myenv) for windows
then (source bin/activate) in linux and myenv\Scripts\activate

Then finally import flask in your project 
from flask import Flask
then do what ever 
source https://flask.palletsprojects.com/en/1.1.x/
 
